channel.title: Delirious614
channel.description:
[CENTER]What is Delirious614?
Delirious614 is a spawn server created by Godofwar and Majd, the admins.
website: [url=http://delirious.webs.com/]Delirious614 Spawn/PK[/url]
What computers does are server support?
We support:
Windows Mac Linux
What do you need to run the server?
You will need the following programs:
Winrar or Winzip Java [JRE]
What commands are there?
::changepassword [newpassword] ::setlevel [id] [lvl] ::bank :: players ::curses [true/false] ::ancients ::moderns ::lunars ::sellitem [id] [amount] ::home ::multi ::barragerunes ::vengrunes ::shop :: pots :onate ::thiev ::save ::resetkdr ::kdr :: points ::empty :ung :eathemote 0 & 1 & 2 ::vote ::votepoints ::claim ::setgender 0 & 1 ::backup ::rules ::reset - reset your combat skills ::yell :ice :icezone ::tradezone ::magebank ::starter ::removestarter +More to come!
